{"tid":1347253,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"上環檢討 每次都要進化！！手足入黎討論！","createTime":"2019-07-22T05:43:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T17:04:35.000Z","uid":90349,"like":298,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":126,"replies":[{"pid":"3a33363b13b9f034ad735ce10ff42cc517b45b30","tid":1347253,"uid":90349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:43:28.000Z","msg":"Too long please read！<br />\n<br />\n琴晚真係好撚勁 有進有退<br />\n<br />\n前線終於有盾陣 開槍後證實<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">遮係可以擋到布袋彈！</span><br />\nd彈pop一聲就跌落地<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">路牌硬淨好多！擋到好多嘢！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">物資鏈係好重要！d欄、竹真係上哂最前</span><br />\n<br />\n但有好多嘢要改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1.敲擊雜物 提高士氣 但係阻礙溝通<br />\n<br />\n啲聲係好鼓舞 但係太大聲會搞到前後講嘢聽唔到<br />\n<br />\n建議: 其實應該好好利用呢樣嘢黎溝通，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">兩下兩下聲=後退、連打=進攻、三長兩短=增加士氣</span></span><br />\n令到前後排溝通更有效率，又加到示氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.物資鏈太多人，傳得慢！<br />\n<br />\n呢樣嘢好多人知，但係大家太想幫手其實係幫倒忙，本身好快傳到，多咗人就慢咗<br />\n<br />\n建議: 一排物資鏈就好似小學做早操咁<span style=\"color: red;\">伸長雙手對位確保距離</span>，係好on9但係work<br />\n<br />\n另外<span style=\"color: red;\">人一多就馬上開第3/第4條隊，唔好</span>下下都2條咁少<br />\n<br />\n3.前線後排溝通不足，想走走唔到<br />\n前線不段為後排爭取時間離開，後面唔走，前面都唔走<br />\n後排唔想掉低前線，前面唔走，後面都唔走<br />\n咁搞法咪大家都想走，但係大家都走唔到，俾狗包抄走唔切好大獲<br />\n<br />\n建議: 現場有哂共識要走嘅時候，<span style=\"color: red;\">前線要用慢慢一步一步後退嘅方式走</span>，咁先爭取到時間，唔好戀戰，後排講到明話俾人包抄，<span style=\"color: red;\">狗唔攻都要退</span>，be water<br />\n後排知道有狗係後面夾，一定<span style=\"color: red;\">揾人上前線講</span>，人傳人傳傳下係會無咗件事！<span style=\"color: red;\">要冷靜配合前線慢慢退</span>，跑得太快，前線就好危險；走太慢，前線就走唔到，同會製造後排味打算走嘅錯覺俾前線<br />\n<br />\n4.有兄弟被tk 一枝膠通掉中頭爆哂江<br />\n建議: <span style=\"color: red;\">無信心掉得準就唔好掉！有信心都上前啲掉！</span><br />\n<br />\n最後，利申:自己身處上環聞到煙但係仲呼吸到嘅位置，呢個po結合一位前線朋友話翻我知嘅情報<br />\n<br />\n元朗嘅事係好撚大獲，呢個仇一定要報，但係唔可以忘記上環一戰，吸取教訓、不段進化、be water<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港、時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"ccb2fdd10fac8e776b4ea0c3aa296d8d230ef514","tid":1347253,"uid":90349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:43:39.000Z","msg":"推啊！"},{"pid":"f961f7c11b6098a2549ba88e8e2c06e4164c4c34","tid":1347253,"uid":90349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:43:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d7326a9292bd5f7af402d1c06a12cc38b3a9434","tid":1347253,"uid":90349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:44:09.000Z","msg":"讓這post推"},{"pid":"da748da09e9e04c6fc0b22f2dc076c72ace9285a","tid":1347253,"uid":99513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:45:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e0550796a5733d13e06bd31259e158d829ead0","tid":1347253,"uid":273676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:45:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f48a15a033840658e5cf9fa3f9369a36e7f07d28","tid":1347253,"uid":90349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:45:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5ed31983c55129adaebdffe2c908514fd4f4365","tid":1347253,"uid":90349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:45:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97836b4c4f67c9558421225774c79b4ef7bae6f6","tid":1347253,"uid":90349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:47:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b124c2dbd75dc056c99b4c76cc3a0024b6140d66","tid":1347253,"uid":90349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:47:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4fcd87988e392c7ea661272fde50deaa662ff482","tid":1347253,"uid":259362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:48:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1845c83893a9c1ec1a9a88146658a10ba38679ef","tid":1347253,"uid":7339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:49:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/